reviewText: Porky's is one of those movies that gets funnier every time you watch it because each time you see it you catch something you missed laughing the first time. Not for children though. It has a lot of nudity and when not outright sexual language, there's sexual innuendos. I got the 3 movie pack so I'd have all 3 of the movies.
Title: Porky's Triple Feature Porky's/Porky's 2/Porky's Revenge

reviewText: I saw all three of these movies when they where first released and probably a dozen times since and they just get better over time, if you don't already have all three then you need these. Great movies at a great price.

Title: Porky's Triple Feature Porky's/Porky's 2/Porky's Revenge

reviewText: We love porky's. I had the first one and wanted the other two. I found this on Amazon and placed a fairly large order of movies. This came first out of all the items and within days of placing the order. It was a used product and it was in fair condition. I watched one movie last night, the second one, and it had a small pause in it but that can easily be buffed out. other than that, so far so good. I think I would order from these people again.
Title: Porky's Triple Feature Porky's/Porky's 2/Porky's Revenge

reviewText: porkys 1 and 2 are incredibly funny and unique, porkys revenge is decent but not as funny, the story and acting are really good and it will make you laugh, follow the boys of angel beach high as they go on a quest to get some lovin at the local brothel with hillarious results.
summary: it doesnt get any better than this!
